title.narrative: Sudan We Cannot Wait

description.narrative: Consortium partners and grassroots women and activists have increased capacity to track progress of gender transformative programs.
Women Rights Activists and Organizations in five regions in Sudan
Women in the Greater Horn of Africa will be leading and defining the political, social cultural and economic agenda.

owner-org.narrative: The Strategic Initiative for Women in the Horn of Africa (SIHA) is a civil society coalition bringing together grassroots women’s rights organizations from Sudan, South Sudan, Somalia, Somaliland, Djibouti, Ethiopia, Eritrea, Kenya and Uganda.
